    "Something similar can be said about the model's choice of preceding the commandments with Roman numerals.",
    "Many depictions throughout history and within popular culture of the commandments represent them on tablets prominently featuring Roman numerals.",
    "In this way, GPT-4 clearly echoes the collective cultural voice of its training.",
    "This will be a recurring motif observable in the analyses of most of the models that follow.",
    "At the 0 setting, we expect the most probable, if constrained, output resulting from the model's training."
